title: *$500 off first month's rent!* Tranquil Apartment at Parkway West
posting_body: ['Property Address', '4556 46th Avenue S - 309 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available: 09/03/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', "Sign a lease today and get $500 off your first month's rent!", 'This cozy, third-floor apartment home features an open, Euro-style kitchen with a moveable center island.', "You'll have access to modern-styled appliances, which include your own dishwasher and an in-unit washer and dryer.", 'The large, open great room gives you a lot of space to customize your new home to your liking.', "You'll also be just one floor down from the large community room, which features an outdoor patio with great views of Minneapolis & Saint Paul.", 'Parkway West was built in 2013 and is located at the corner of 46th Avenue and 46th Street in Minneapolis.', 'Your new neighborhood is right off the Ford Parkway Bridge and across from Minnehaha Falls, Minnehaha Park and Pavilion/band shell.', 'The one and two-bedroom apartment homes at Parkway West bring Euro-style custom design features into a beautiful open floor plan.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Fitness Center', 'Community lounge and patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Keyless Entry', 'Cats Welcome', 'Smoke-Free Living', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 736', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,495.00', 'Available: 09/03/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
